'''Light electric vehicles''' are [[electric vehicle]]s with 2 or 4 wheels powered by a battery, fuel cell, or hybrid-powered, and generally weighing less than {{convert|100|kg|lbs}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://extraenergy.org/main.php?language=es&category=information&subcateg=99&id=2285|title=Light Electric Vehicle Association (LEVA) established|work=ExtraEnergy.org}}</ref> Examples include [[electric bicycle]]s, [[electric kick scooter]]s. In Europe these are classified under the L category.

